    "body": "On Linux, the application icon depends on putting a file in `/usr/share/applications`, which we can't practically do from Python package installation - that's up to distro packagers. The Debian/Ubuntu packages for IPython seem to have this sorted out correctly.\n\nI think it should be possible on Windows, but I don't know what's required.\n"
